json-server and vite uses localhost instead of 127.0.0.1 or 0.0.0.0
localhost is converted to an ipv6 address ([::1]:port) instead of an ipv4
firefox resolves localhost to 127.0.0.1 only
chrome resolves localhost to 127.0.0.1 and ::1

https://github.com/vitejs/vite/issues/12583#issuecomment-1484099103
https://github.com/nodejs/node/issues/40537
